dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Patrick Allen. May I have your name, please?
Hello Patrick, my name is Marie Murphy.
Nice to meet you, Marie. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is five six two four nine.
Thank you, Marie. Additionally, could you verify your date of birth for security purposes?
Of course, my date of birth is the twenty second of September, nineteen ninety eight.
Thank you for confirming, Marie. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today regarding your policy?
Yes, I wanted to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
I can assist you with that. Please provide me with the make, model, and year of the vehicle you'd like to add.
It's a red Toyota Corolla, two zero one eight.
Thank you for the information, Marie. I will update your policy accordingly. If you have any more questions, feel free to ask. Thank you for your time today.
